<section>
<section id="slide-orge69e078">
<h2 id="orge69e078">Life expectancy and income</h2>
<ul>
<li>Men in the top 1% live 14.6 years longer than men in the lowest 1%</li>
<li>Women in the top 1% live 10.1 years longer than women in the lowest 1%</li>
<li>Gap between men and women lower at high incomes</li>
<li>How has this changed over time?</li>

</ul>

</section>
</section>
<section>
<section id="slide-org40f3004">
<h2 id="org40f3004"></h2>

