<section>
<section id="slide-org15fbdbc">
<h2 id="org15fbdbc">Change in life expectancy</h2>
<ul>
<li>Life expectancy across most income groups growing</li>
<li>Growing slowly for people low in the distribution, higher for the wealthy</li>
<li>Poorest 5% do not appear to be living longer at all</li>

</ul>

</section>
</section>
<section>
<section id="slide-org0b24af0">
