</section>
</section>
<section>
<section id="slide-org5993506">
<h2 id="org5993506">Causes</h2>
<ul>
<li>Income highly correlated with mortality</li>
<li>Cannot explain everything, income for whites shows similar patterns as other groups</li>
<li>Case and Deaton suggest "cumulative deprivation" (fewer prospects in life)</li>

</ul>

</section>
</section>
<section>
<section id="slide-org28840d9">
<h2 id="org28840d9"></h2>

<div class="figure">
<p><img src="./img/case_deaton_fig21.png" alt="case_deaton_fig21.png" />
</p>
